1
00:00:01,340 --> 00:00:03,906
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
All right, the lighthouse</b></Default>

2
00:00:03,930 --> 00:00:05,586
<Default><b>and its barrier should be
under our control now.</b></Default>

3
00:00:05,610 --> 00:00:09,415
<Default><b>And the embers of rebellion
have been fanned into a flame.</b></Default>

4
00:00:09,439 --> 00:00:12,405
<Default><b>Now, before we try tackling
any other problems</b></Default>

5
00:00:12,429 --> 00:00:14,286
<Default><b>I want to go
over some things.</b></Default>

6
00:00:14,310 --> 00:00:16,706
<Default><b>First of all... hold up.</b></Default>

7
00:00:16,730 --> 00:00:18,965
<Default><b>What's with
the pitiful expressions?</b></Default>

8
00:00:18,989 --> 00:00:22,405
<Default><b>I thought you'd be more excited
about all of this happening.</b></Default>

9
00:00:22,429 --> 00:00:23,646
<Default><b>I'm so sorry.</b></Default>

10
00:00:23,670 --> 00:00:25,846
<Default><b>It's just that...</b></Default>

11
00:00:25,870 --> 00:00:27,596
<Default><b>[AIDE] W... water!</b></Default>

12
00:00:27,620 --> 00:00:30,296
<Default><b>Was it really necessary
to challenge all of them</b></Default>

13
00:00:30,320 --> 00:00:31,826
<Default><b>to a drinking
competition?</b></Default>

14
00:00:31,850 --> 00:00:32,827
<Default><b>I did?</b></Default>

15
00:00:32,851 --> 00:00:34,265
<Default><b>Goodness grief.</b></Default>

16
00:00:34,289 --> 00:00:35,985
<Default><b>At this rate</b></Default>

17
00:00:36,009 --> 00:00:37,286
<Default><b>[scoffs]</b></Default>

18
00:00:37,310 --> 00:00:39,896
<Default><b>Well, start shaking off
those hangovers</b></Default>

19
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:42,816
<Default><b>'cause we don't have time
to waste here.</b></Default>

20
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:45,066
<Default><b>[FILO groans]</b></Default>

21
00:00:45,090 --> 00:00:48,055
<Default><b>If you can</b></Default>

22
00:00:48,079 --> 00:00:50,226
<Default><b>exactly where
the emperor should be.</b></Default>

23
00:00:50,250 --> 00:00:54,555
<Default><b>We can negotiate
or kill them</b></Default>

24
00:00:54,579 --> 00:00:56,326
<Default><b>[RALUVA]
I'd be happy to.</b></Default>

25
00:00:56,350 --> 00:00:59,455
<Default><b>The current emperor of Q'ten Lo
resides here, in the capital.</b></Default>

26
00:00:59,479 --> 00:01:01,085
<Default><b>Really?</b></Default>

27
00:01:01,109 --> 00:01:03,015
<Default><b>That's not where they lived
back when I was living here.</b></Default>

28
00:01:03,039 --> 00:01:04,415
<Default><b>Well, you see</b></Default>

29
00:01:04,439 --> 00:01:06,855
<Default><b>took over the throne</b></Default>

30
00:01:06,879 --> 00:01:08,295
<Default><b>So that's how it is.</b></Default>

31
00:01:08,319 --> 00:01:11,325
<Default><b>But the home of the old
emperor still exists.</b></Default>

32
00:01:11,349 --> 00:01:13,635
<Default><b>It's just called
the "old capital" now.</b></Default>

33
00:01:13,659 --> 00:01:16,676
<Default><b>Our best bet would be
to start our conquest there.</b></Default>

34
00:01:16,700 --> 00:01:17,715
<Default><b>Oh, wow.</b></Default>

35
00:01:17,739 --> 00:01:18,976
<Default><b>You've thought
about this.</b></Default>

36
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,135
<Default><b>What do you mean?</b></Default>

37
00:01:20,159 --> 00:01:22,896
<Default><b>You see</b></Default>

38
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:26,116
<Default><b>is where the previous emperors
would take the royal throne.</b></Default>

39
00:01:26,140 --> 00:01:28,726
<Default><b>So if Raphtalia were
to do the ritual there</b></Default>

40
00:01:28,750 --> 00:01:30,426
<Default><b>she'd be able to use
the blessings</b></Default>

41
00:01:30,450 --> 00:01:31,646
<Default><b>like any other emperor.</b></Default>

42
00:01:31,670 --> 00:01:33,646
<Default><b>- Oh.
- Pretty smart.</b></Default>

43
00:01:33,670 --> 00:01:35,855
<Default><b>Having an advantage like
that is bound to help us</b></Default>

44
00:01:35,879 --> 00:01:37,575
<Default><b>in any of our
future battles.</b></Default>

45
00:01:37,599 --> 00:01:39,045
<Default><b>It's strange though.</b></Default>

46
00:01:39,069 --> 00:01:41,355
<Default><b>Why would they go
and abandon the old capital?</b></Default>

47
00:01:41,379 --> 00:01:43,045
<Default><b>It's so risky.</b></Default>

48
00:01:43,069 --> 00:01:46,195
<Default><b>Yes, it is, but the emperor's
puppet master of an advisor</b></Default>

49
00:01:46,219 --> 00:01:48,226
<Default><b>Makina</b></Default>

50
00:01:48,250 --> 00:01:49,396
<Default><b>Makina?</b></Default>

51
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:51,346
<Default><b>Does that mean
she's still around?</b></Default>

52
00:01:51,370 --> 00:01:52,786
<Default><b>Unfortunately, yes.</b></Default>

53
00:01:52,810 --> 00:01:54,665
<Default><b>- And she's evil.
- Evil, huh?</b></Default>

54
00:01:54,689 --> 00:01:55,855
<Default><b>Great.</b></Default>

55
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:57,575
<Default><b>In that case</b></Default>

56
00:01:57,599 --> 00:01:59,575
<Default><b>a pretty good chance
she comes after us</b></Default>

57
00:01:59,599 --> 00:02:01,266
<Default><b>now that we've taken
her lighthouse.</b></Default>

58
00:02:01,290 --> 00:02:03,445
<Default><b>Meaning we need to be
prepared to deal with her.</b></Default>

59
00:02:03,469 --> 00:02:04,656
<Default><b>[RALUVA] Yes, sir!</b></Default>

60
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,766
<Default><b>Now then</b></Default>

61
00:02:06,790 --> 00:02:09,806
<Default><b>we should have Raphtalia
wear her miko outfit</b></Default>

62
00:02:09,830 --> 00:02:12,695
<Default><b>and have a parade
to raise the people's spirits.</b></Default>

63
00:02:12,719 --> 00:02:15,096
<Default><b>I understand
your thinking behind that</b></Default>

64
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:18,605
<Default><b>but why would me wearing my
miko outfit help boost morale?</b></Default>

65
00:02:18,629 --> 00:02:19,825
<Default><b>It looks good!</b></Default>

66
00:02:19,849 --> 00:02:21,280
<Default><b>Raph!</b></Default>

67
00:02:23,159 --> 00:02:25,045
<Default><b>Uh. [Laughs awkwardly]</b></Default>

68
00:02:25,069 --> 00:02:26,586
<Default><b>[distant boom]</b></Default>

69
00:02:26,610 --> 00:02:27,730
<Default><b>Now what?</b></Default>

70
00:02:28,659 --> 00:02:33,056
<Default><b>THE RISING OF
THE SHIELD HERO</b></Default>

71
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:35,056
<Default><b>EPISODE 8: OROCHI</b></Default>

72
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:37,135
<Default><b>[stirring music]</b></Default>

73
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:39,135
<Default><b>They're attacking
us already?</b></Default>

74
00:02:39,159 --> 00:02:41,425
<Default><b>That or the big party
that was going on in town</b></Default>

75
00:02:41,449 --> 00:02:42,966
<Default><b>just got way
out of hand.</b></Default>

76
00:02:42,990 --> 00:02:45,036
<Default><b>But it didn't sound
like either of those.</b></Default>

77
00:02:45,060 --> 00:02:47,726
<Default><b>I can feel a strange flow
of energy now.</b></Default>

78
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:49,086
<Default><b>What was that?</b></Default>

79
00:02:49,110 --> 00:02:51,205
<Default><b>Did anyone else
hear that sound?</b></Default>

80
00:02:51,229 --> 00:02:53,256
<Default><b>I don't see how
they couldn't.</b></Default>

81
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,615
<Default><b>[chirping]</b></Default>

82
00:02:54,639 --> 00:02:55,976
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

83
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:58,135
<Default><b>Look, over there!</b></Default>

84
00:02:58,159 --> 00:03:00,786
<Default><b>[eerie music]</b></Default>

85
00:03:00,810 --> 00:03:03,156
<Default><b>That's where
the old burial mound is.</b></Default>

86
00:03:03,180 --> 00:03:05,175
<Default><b>What's going on?</b></Default>

87
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:07,205
<Default><b>[SOLDIER] M... monsters!</b></Default>

88
00:03:07,229 --> 00:03:10,726
<Default><b>I can't see
everything clearly</b></Default>

89
00:03:10,750 --> 00:03:12,990
<Default><b>it looks like multiple
snake monsters.</b></Default>

90
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,056
<Default><b>Snake monsters?</b></Default>

91
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,057
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

92
00:03:16,081 --> 00:03:18,175
<Default><b>[MURAMASA]
Hey, kid.</b></Default>

93
00:03:18,199 --> 00:03:20,735
<Default><b>I guess I shouldn't be too
surprised that the government</b></Default>

94
00:03:20,759 --> 00:03:22,425
<Default><b>isn't holding back
against us</b></Default>

95
00:03:22,449 --> 00:03:25,096
<Default><b>but freeing a monster
from its seal?</b></Default>

96
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:27,936
<Default><b>That seems a little
overboard, even for them.</b></Default>

97
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,175
<Default><b>Its seal?</b></Default>

98
00:03:29,199 --> 00:03:30,846
<Default><b>Do you know anything
about this?</b></Default>

99
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:32,936
<Default><b>I don't answer questions
from other men!</b></Default>

100
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:35,346
<Default><b>And why would I tell someone
who's too dumb to make a harem</b></Default>

101
00:03:35,370 --> 00:03:36,455
<Default><b>when he obviously could?</b></Default>

102
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:37,545
<Default><b>This idiot!</b></Default>

103
00:03:37,569 --> 00:03:39,756
<Default><b>[grumbles]</b></Default>

104
00:03:39,780 --> 00:03:41,156
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

105
00:03:41,180 --> 00:03:42,556
<Default><b>All right then.</b></Default>

106
00:03:42,580 --> 00:03:44,656
<Default><b>How's about telling
little ol' me about it?</b></Default>

107
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,156
<Default><b>Anything for you, dear!</b></Default>

108
00:03:46,180 --> 00:03:48,226
<Default><b>Well, I'll tell you
whatever you want.</b></Default>

109
00:03:48,250 --> 00:03:50,596
<Default><b>There's an old ruin
in the mountains over there.</b></Default>

110
00:03:50,620 --> 00:03:52,036
<Default><b>Within those same ruins</b></Default>

111
00:03:52,060 --> 00:03:54,075
<Default><b>a monster that once brought
disastrous harm</b></Default>

112
00:03:54,099 --> 00:03:56,145
<Default><b>to this country
is sealed away.</b></Default>

113
00:03:56,169 --> 00:03:58,015
<Default><b>However, the legend
the government's peddled</b></Default>

114
00:03:58,039 --> 00:04:00,036
<Default><b>is that the emperor
defeated it.</b></Default>

115
00:04:00,060 --> 00:04:02,605
<Default><b>But in reality</b></Default>

116
00:04:02,629 --> 00:04:05,765
<Default><b>Up till now, I had only
ever heard it was defeated.</b></Default>

117
00:04:05,789 --> 00:04:08,496
<Default><b>Well, considering
the location of the ruins</b></Default>

118
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,675
<Default><b>it makes sense only
a few know the truth</b></Default>

119
00:04:10,699 --> 00:04:12,126
<Default><b>about the
monster's fate.</b></Default>

120
00:04:12,150 --> 00:04:14,165
<Default><b>But I am the government's
favorite blacksmith</b></Default>

121
00:04:14,189 --> 00:04:15,626
<Default><b>so of course I know.</b></Default>

122
00:04:15,650 --> 00:04:17,995
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Why lie
and say it was defeated?</b></Default>

123
00:04:18,019 --> 00:04:19,665
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

124
00:04:19,689 --> 00:04:22,255
<Default><b>They said that the reason they
sealed it here was in order</b></Default>

125
00:04:22,279 --> 00:04:25,076
<Default><b>to help strengthen the barrier
that separates Q'ten Lo</b></Default>

126
00:04:25,100 --> 00:04:26,886
<Default><b>from the rest
of the world.</b></Default>

127
00:04:26,910 --> 00:04:29,076
<Default><b>It acts as a
protective god.</b></Default>

128
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:30,665
<Default><b>There are ruins
just like the one</b></Default>

129
00:04:30,689 --> 00:04:32,786
<Default><b>I mentioned scattered
across the country.</b></Default>

130
00:04:32,810 --> 00:04:34,745
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] So you're saying
the government</b></Default>

131
00:04:34,769 --> 00:04:37,886
<Default><b>has multiple monsters sealed
away and revived one of them?</b></Default>

132
00:04:37,910 --> 00:04:40,255
<Default><b>[MURAMASA]
Yes, exactly.</b></Default>

133
00:04:40,279 --> 00:04:42,365
<Default><b>And there's
another problem.</b></Default>

134
00:04:42,389 --> 00:04:46,536
<Default><b>Well, this did happen a little
while ago, but listen to this.</b></Default>

135
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,266
<Default><b>The current emperor</b></Default>

136
00:04:48,290 --> 00:04:50,156
<Default><b>decided they really liked
all the monsters</b></Default>

137
00:04:50,180 --> 00:04:53,016
<Default><b>and wanted to reduce the strain
on our protector gods.</b></Default>

138
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:55,495
<Default><b>The best idea that
they could come up with</b></Default>

139
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:58,175
<Default><b>in order to do that was
granting them the blessings and</b></Default>

140
00:04:58,199 --> 00:05:00,065
<Default><b>the Sakura
Emperor's stones.</b></Default>

141
00:05:00,089 --> 00:05:01,435
<Default><b>Are they idiots?</b></Default>

142
00:05:01,459 --> 00:05:03,125
<Default><b>They went and strengthened
a giant monster</b></Default>

143
00:05:03,149 --> 00:05:04,745
<Default><b>that brought disaster
to their country</b></Default>

144
00:05:04,769 --> 00:05:06,795
<Default><b>then chose to revive it?</b></Default>

145
00:05:06,819 --> 00:05:10,266
<Default><b>We could barely beat that
bear creature from yesterday!</b></Default>

146
00:05:10,290 --> 00:05:12,279
<Default><b>Master Naofumi</b></Default>

147
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:16,815
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] It's a pain</b></Default>

148
00:05:16,839 --> 00:05:17,915
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

149
00:05:17,939 --> 00:05:19,476
<Default><b>What if the first
thing you do</b></Default>

150
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:21,875
<Default><b>as emperor is defeating
a giant monster</b></Default>

151
00:05:21,899 --> 00:05:24,216
<Default><b>like that, one that
the government intentionally</b></Default>

152
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,456
<Default><b>freed to hurt
its citizens</b></Default>

153
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:29,406
<Default><b>the entire country
knows about it?</b></Default>

154
00:05:29,430 --> 00:05:31,855
<Default><b>Oh, if that happens...</b></Default>

155
00:05:31,879 --> 00:05:33,406
<Default><b>Mhm.</b></Default>

156
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:35,466
<Default><b>It will show the people
their government hates them</b></Default>

157
00:05:35,490 --> 00:05:37,865
<Default><b>and that a revolutionary
army is here now</b></Default>

158
00:05:37,889 --> 00:05:39,355
<Default><b>to fight on
their behalf.</b></Default>

159
00:05:39,379 --> 00:05:40,906
<Default><b>[SOLDIER 1]
Revolutionaries?</b></Default>

160
00:05:40,930 --> 00:05:42,826
<Default><b>[SOLDIER 2] Now, that's
something I can get behind.</b></Default>

161
00:05:42,850 --> 00:05:45,875
<Default><b>But for this to work</b></Default>

162
00:05:45,899 --> 00:05:47,446
<Default><b>before it reaches town!</b></Default>

163
00:05:47,470 --> 00:05:48,466
<Default><b>Gaelion!</b></Default>

164
00:05:48,490 --> 00:05:50,675
<Default><b>[squawking]</b></Default>

165
00:05:50,699 --> 00:05:52,336
<Default><b>Speed's our priority.</b></Default>

166
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:55,125
<Default><b>We'll split up and have Gaelion
and Filo bring us there.</b></Default>

167
00:05:55,149 --> 00:05:56,629
<Default><b>Sounds good to me.</b></Default>

168
00:05:57,610 --> 00:05:59,485
<Default><b>I don't know if brother
will help much</b></Default>

169
00:05:59,509 --> 00:06:01,026
<Default><b>but we're coming
along to fight it.</b></Default>

170
00:06:01,050 --> 00:06:02,027
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

171
00:06:02,051 --> 00:06:03,946
<Default><b>Wait, Atla!</b></Default>

172
00:06:03,970 --> 00:06:05,355
<Default><b>[wings flapping]</b></Default>

173
00:06:05,379 --> 00:06:08,656
<Default><b>[stirring music]</b></Default>

174
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,745
<Default><b>Go on.</b></Default>

175
00:06:09,769 --> 00:06:11,005
<Default><b>We'll follow your lead.</b></Default>

176
00:06:11,029 --> 00:06:12,516
<Default><b>Show us the way.</b></Default>

177
00:06:12,540 --> 00:06:14,985
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

178
00:06:15,009 --> 00:06:17,396
<Default><b>No way is Gaelion
beating me there!</b></Default>

179
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:19,605
<Default><b>Ah!</b></Default>

180
00:06:19,629 --> 00:06:21,976
<Default><b>[MURAMASA] Hey, ladies</b></Default>

181
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,976
<Default><b>just remember, you can feed
that loser to the monsters</b></Default>

182
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,305
<Default><b>and run away!</b></Default>

183
00:06:26,329 --> 00:06:28,415
<Default><b>Come on, master</b></Default>

184
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:29,599
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

185
00:06:31,930 --> 00:06:35,360
<Default><b>[thrilling music]</b></Default>

186
00:06:37,810 --> 00:06:39,735
<Default><b>I have a feeling
a hydra will be</b></Default>

187
00:06:39,759 --> 00:06:41,685
<Default><b>rather difficult
to deal with.</b></Default>

188
00:06:41,709 --> 00:06:43,286
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Seven and eight.</b></Default>

189
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:45,136
<Default><b>It's not multiple
monsters.</b></Default>

190
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,505
<Default><b>You're right, Gaelion.</b></Default>

191
00:06:46,529 --> 00:06:48,929
<Default><b>It's an eight-headed
hydra we're fighting.</b></Default>

192
00:06:50,350 --> 00:06:53,485
<Default><b>[SADEENA] Holy ropes
and the Sakura Emperor's Stone.</b></Default>

193
00:06:53,509 --> 00:06:55,136
<Default><b>We can assume
it's been blessed.</b></Default>

194
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:58,466
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] So they did go out
of their way to power it up.</b></Default>

195
00:06:58,490 --> 00:06:59,850
<Default><b>[whoosh]</b></Default>

196
00:07:02,579 --> 00:07:05,855
<Default><b>With the Sakura Emperor's
Stone barrier and the blessing</b></Default>

197
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:08,196
<Default><b>that hydra is going to weaken
the hero's protection</b></Default>

198
00:07:08,220 --> 00:07:10,115
<Default><b>if we end up
getting too close to it.</b></Default>

199
00:07:10,139 --> 00:07:13,726
<Default><b>We have to destroy it
before it reaches the town.</b></Default>

200
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:15,425
<Default><b>[humming]</b></Default>

201
00:07:15,449 --> 00:07:17,805
<Default><b>[GAELION] I'm beginning
to sense draconic power.</b></Default>

202
00:07:17,829 --> 00:07:20,735
<Default><b>The water dragon may
be trying to help us.</b></Default>

203
00:07:20,759 --> 00:07:24,305
<Default><b>Well, that's awfully nice
of him, but...</b></Default>

204
00:07:24,329 --> 00:07:26,346
<Default><b>It's not going
to last forever.</b></Default>

205
00:07:26,370 --> 00:07:28,206
<Default><b>Which means
we have to finish it.</b></Default>

206
00:07:28,230 --> 00:07:29,665
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

207
00:07:29,689 --> 00:07:32,805
<Default><b>I'll make use of the Sakura
Sphere of Influence.</b></Default>

208
00:07:32,829 --> 00:07:34,226
<Default><b>[whoosh]</b></Default>

209
00:07:34,250 --> 00:07:36,125
<Default><b>[boom]</b></Default>

210
00:07:36,149 --> 00:07:39,516
<Default><b>Itsuki, where's your Sakura
Emperor's Stone weapon?</b></Default>

211
00:07:39,540 --> 00:07:40,555
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Here!</b></Default>

212
00:07:40,579 --> 00:07:42,156
<Default><b>[RISHIA]
It's ready to go!</b></Default>

213
00:07:42,180 --> 00:07:44,625
<Default><b>Hey, I can help
too, you know.</b></Default>

214
00:07:44,649 --> 00:07:47,326
<Default><b>The blacksmiths gave me
this earlier!</b></Default>

215
00:07:47,350 --> 00:07:48,735
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I see.</b></Default>

216
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:50,375
<Default><b>So this is making up
for the hero</b></Default>

217
00:07:50,399 --> 00:07:52,536
<Default><b>stat buffs that
were nullified.</b></Default>

218
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,456
<Default><b>You did a
fine job, Elhart.</b></Default>

219
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:56,326
<Default><b>[ATLA] Quit squirming.</b></Default>

220
00:07:56,350 --> 00:07:59,216
<Default><b>Just give me
one of the stones</b></Default>

221
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:01,016
<Default><b>But didn't he
give you one, too?</b></Default>

222
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,295
<Default><b>Yes, but I didn't like
the way</b></Default>

223
00:08:02,319 --> 00:08:03,776
<Default><b>that creep was
touching my hands</b></Default>

224
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,466
<Default><b>so I went and threw
it away right after.</b></Default>

225
00:08:05,490 --> 00:08:07,216
<Default><b>That's enough.</b></Default>

226
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:10,096
<Default><b>Atla, you're to stay back and
help Itsuki, S'yne, and Rishia.</b></Default>

227
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,375
<Default><b>Got it?</b></Default>

228
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:12,376
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

229
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:13,555
<Default><b>Oh, I understand.</b></Default>

230
00:08:13,579 --> 00:08:14,925
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

231
00:08:14,949 --> 00:08:17,216
<Default><b>Sakura Sphere
of Influence</b></Default>

232
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,600
<Default><b>[magical beams]</b></Default>

233
00:08:19,949 --> 00:08:22,185
<Default><b>[roars]</b></Default>

234
00:08:22,209 --> 00:08:24,050
<Default><b>Ready or not,
here I come!</b></Default>

235
00:08:25,370 --> 00:08:27,586
<Default><b>[boom]</b></Default>

236
00:08:27,610 --> 00:08:29,656
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
It doesn't have much defense</b></Default>

237
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:33,855
<Default><b>but Gaelion
called it a hydra</b></Default>

238
00:08:33,879 --> 00:08:35,145
<Default><b>[squelching]</b></Default>

239
00:08:35,169 --> 00:08:37,546
<Default><b>I knew it.</b></Default>

240
00:08:37,570 --> 00:08:39,066
<Default><b>I'm not done yet!</b></Default>

241
00:08:39,090 --> 00:08:40,446
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

242
00:08:40,470 --> 00:08:42,355
<Default><b>[FOHL] Hope you don't
mind me taking a lift!</b></Default>

243
00:08:42,379 --> 00:08:43,379
<Default><b>Ah!</b></Default>

244
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:46,440
<Default><b>[boom]</b></Default>

245
00:08:49,539 --> 00:08:50,596
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

246
00:08:50,620 --> 00:08:51,806
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Aim for the torso!</b></Default>

247
00:08:51,830 --> 00:08:53,196
<Default><b>I think it's weak there!</b></Default>

248
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:54,220
<Default><b>OK!</b></Default>

249
00:08:58,139 --> 00:08:59,139
<Default><b>Ah!</b></Default>

250
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,759
<Default><b>[clank]</b></Default>

251
00:09:03,350 --> 00:09:04,720
<Default><b>It's strong!</b></Default>

252
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,240
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

253
00:09:11,159 --> 00:09:12,620
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

254
00:09:17,980 --> 00:09:19,440
<Default><b>[flames blaze]</b></Default>

255
00:09:22,769 --> 00:09:26,696
<Default><b>[GAELION] It's absorbing
part of the Dragon Vein.</b></Default>

256
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,796
<Default><b>We can't dispel it
unless we cut off</b></Default>

257
00:09:28,820 --> 00:09:32,105
<Default><b>all eight heads that are
generating the barrier at once.</b></Default>

258
00:09:32,129 --> 00:09:33,326
<Default><b>What's the plan?</b></Default>

259
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:35,096
<Default><b>We don't have time
to wait around.</b></Default>

260
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,097
<Default><b>I know!</b></Default>

261
00:09:36,121 --> 00:09:37,676
<Default><b>Everyone, listen!</b></Default>

262
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:40,625
<Default><b>Raphtalia will be the first
to attack the hydra.</b></Default>

263
00:09:40,649 --> 00:09:43,556
<Default><b>After she destroys
its magical protection</b></Default>

264
00:09:43,580 --> 00:09:46,586
<Default><b>we'll chop off all its heads
at once and finish it off!</b></Default>

265
00:09:46,610 --> 00:09:47,587
<Default><b>Got it?</b></Default>

266
00:09:47,611 --> 00:09:48,875
<Default><b>Understood.</b></Default>

267
00:09:48,899 --> 00:09:51,586
<Default><b>Sadeena, do a choral
magic spell with me!</b></Default>

268
00:09:51,610 --> 00:09:53,130
<Default><b>Ready when you are!</b></Default>

269
00:09:54,279 --> 00:09:55,855
<Default><b>Go!</b></Default>

270
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:57,655
<Default><b>[whoosh]</b></Default>

271
00:09:57,679 --> 00:09:58,785
<Default><b>[roars]</b></Default>

272
00:09:58,809 --> 00:10:00,750
<Default><b>[boom]</b></Default>

273
00:10:04,179 --> 00:10:06,916
<Default><b>Supreme Ultimate
Slash of Destiny!</b></Default>

274
00:10:06,940 --> 00:10:08,350
<Default><b>[squelch]</b></Default>

275
00:10:10,230 --> 00:10:11,580
<Default><b>[chittering]</b></Default>

276
00:10:12,570 --> 00:10:13,966
<Default><b>[flames blaze]</b></Default>

277
00:10:13,990 --> 00:10:16,005
<Default><b>Filo, trigger
the hydra's barrier!</b></Default>

278
00:10:16,029 --> 00:10:17,309
<Default><b>[FILO] On it!</b></Default>

279
00:10:18,389 --> 00:10:19,389
<Default><b>Ah!</b></Default>

280
00:10:21,269 --> 00:10:22,655
<Default><b>[boom]</b></Default>

281
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:24,556
<Default><b>[chittering]</b></Default>

282
00:10:24,580 --> 00:10:27,005
<Default><b>The Sakura Emperor's Stone
should now be nullified.</b></Default>

283
00:10:27,029 --> 00:10:28,006
<Default><b>Good.</b></Default>

284
00:10:28,030 --> 00:10:29,485
<Default><b>Now it's our turn!</b></Default>

285
00:10:29,509 --> 00:10:31,155
<Default><b>Summon Thunder God!</b></Default>

286
00:10:31,179 --> 00:10:33,105
<Default><b>[electric crackle]</b></Default>

287
00:10:33,129 --> 00:10:36,176
<Default><b>I'm not letting you guys
have all the fun!</b></Default>

288
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,605
<Default><b>[boom]</b></Default>

289
00:10:37,629 --> 00:10:38,629
<Default><b>Ah!</b></Default>

290
00:10:39,629 --> 00:10:42,826
<Default><b>Eagle piercing shot!</b></Default>

291
00:10:42,850 --> 00:10:47,666
<Default><b>Hengen Muso Secret
Technique, Rolling Spin!</b></Default>

292
00:10:47,690 --> 00:10:49,015
<Default><b>[boom]</b></Default>

293
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:50,785
<Default><b>[wires squeaking]</b></Default>

294
00:10:50,809 --> 00:10:53,115
<Default><b>Critical wire!</b></Default>

295
00:10:53,139 --> 00:10:55,009
<Default><b>[squelch]</b></Default>

296
00:10:57,340 --> 00:10:58,317
<Default><b>Drifa.</b></Default>

297
00:10:58,341 --> 00:11:00,625
<Default><b>Chain Lightning!</b></Default>

298
00:11:00,649 --> 00:11:02,426
<Default><b>[electric crackle]</b></Default>

299
00:11:02,450 --> 00:11:04,285
<Default><b>Hurry, Raphtalia!</b></Default>

300
00:11:04,309 --> 00:11:06,785
<Default><b>Stardust Blade!</b></Default>

301
00:11:06,809 --> 00:11:08,755
<Default><b>[Shing]</b></Default>

302
00:11:08,779 --> 00:11:10,740
<Default><b>[squelch,
resounding thud]</b></Default>

303
00:11:17,629 --> 00:11:20,285
<Default><b>That was a whole lot easier
than I thought it'd be.</b></Default>

304
00:11:20,309 --> 00:11:21,826
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Yeah, no kidding.</b></Default>

305
00:11:21,850 --> 00:11:23,206
<Default><b>[RALUVA] Raphtalia!</b></Default>

306
00:11:23,230 --> 00:11:25,710
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Well, look
who decided to show up.</b></Default>

307
00:11:32,059 --> 00:11:33,340
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

308
00:11:34,549 --> 00:11:36,529
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

309
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:39,865
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] What the?</b></Default>

310
00:11:39,889 --> 00:11:41,285
<Default><b>This is certainly
strange.</b></Default>

311
00:11:41,309 --> 00:11:42,549
<Default><b>It's like...</b></Default>

312
00:11:43,909 --> 00:11:45,145
<Default><b>[squelching]</b></Default>

313
00:11:45,169 --> 00:11:46,796
<Default><b>It isn't finished
with us.</b></Default>

314
00:11:46,820 --> 00:11:48,446
<Default><b>Run away!</b></Default>

315
00:11:48,470 --> 00:11:50,426
<Default><b>[panicked screams]</b></Default>

316
00:11:50,450 --> 00:11:53,899
<Default><b>[ominous music]</b></Default>

317
00:11:54,899 --> 00:11:57,365
<Default><b>[boom]</b></Default>

318
00:11:57,389 --> 00:11:59,035
<Default><b>Meteor Shield!</b></Default>

319
00:11:59,059 --> 00:12:00,505
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

320
00:12:00,529 --> 00:12:07,355
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

321
00:12:07,379 --> 00:12:08,416
<Default><b>The barrier!</b></Default>

322
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,666
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
This is bad.</b></Default>

323
00:12:09,690 --> 00:12:11,405
<Default><b>[GAELION] It would appear
our enemy</b></Default>

324
00:12:11,429 --> 00:12:13,549
<Default><b>is more formidable
than we thought.</b></Default>

325
00:12:14,950 --> 00:12:15,926
<Default><b>[chittering]</b></Default>

326
00:12:15,950 --> 00:12:16,927
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] What?</b></Default>

327
00:12:16,951 --> 00:12:22,385
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

328
00:12:22,409 --> 00:12:24,706
<Default><b>It's back, but it
looks purple now!</b></Default>

329
00:12:24,730 --> 00:12:27,416
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Is this one different
from the one we fought before?</b></Default>

330
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:30,576
<Default><b>[GAELION] Both it and the one
before aren't the real body.</b></Default>

331
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:33,765
<Default><b>Destroying the real one
won't be so easy.</b></Default>

332
00:12:33,789 --> 00:12:35,669
<Default><b>I'll stop it from
advancing!</b></Default>

333
00:12:37,110 --> 00:12:38,299
<Default><b>Me too!</b></Default>

334
00:12:40,370 --> 00:12:42,336
<Default><b>[hissing]</b></Default>

335
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:44,735
<Default><b>Whatever happened, it
seems stronger than before.</b></Default>

336
00:12:44,759 --> 00:12:46,186
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

337
00:12:46,210 --> 00:12:47,875
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Is there some
way to deal with this?</b></Default>

338
00:12:47,899 --> 00:12:49,655
<Default><b>[GAELION]
It's a type of dragon.</b></Default>

339
00:12:49,679 --> 00:12:51,105
<Default><b>I'm sure of that.</b></Default>

340
00:12:51,129 --> 00:12:54,056
<Default><b>And you know a little
about dragons, right?</b></Default>

341
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,466
<Default><b>Then there's a core.</b></Default>

342
00:12:55,490 --> 00:12:57,995
<Default><b>So that's why the last
one didn't have one.</b></Default>

343
00:12:58,019 --> 00:13:01,556
<Default><b>Which means the real core
is inside of there.</b></Default>

344
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:03,745
<Default><b>Meaning our best bet is
to keep those monsters</b></Default>

345
00:13:03,769 --> 00:13:06,076
<Default><b>from exploding while we
steal the core back, right?</b></Default>

346
00:13:06,100 --> 00:13:07,586
<Default><b>[GAELION] Yes.</b></Default>

347
00:13:07,610 --> 00:13:09,436
<Default><b>Only the empty shells
will remain.</b></Default>

348
00:13:09,460 --> 00:13:12,066
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] What do we do with
the core after we get it?</b></Default>

349
00:13:12,090 --> 00:13:14,186
<Default><b>[GAELION] I, the weakest
Dragon Emperor</b></Default>

350
00:13:14,210 --> 00:13:15,556
<Default><b>will have
to restrain it.</b></Default>

351
00:13:15,580 --> 00:13:17,076
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Can you?</b></Default>

352
00:13:17,100 --> 00:13:18,495
<Default><b>[GAELION]
If it's just the core</b></Default>

353
00:13:18,519 --> 00:13:21,505
<Default><b>even the weakest of us
should be able to do it.</b></Default>

354
00:13:21,529 --> 00:13:22,506
<Default><b>Ah!</b></Default>

355
00:13:22,530 --> 00:13:23,995
<Default><b>[slice, squelch]</b></Default>

356
00:13:24,019 --> 00:13:25,476
<Default><b>[lightning crashes]</b></Default>

357
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:28,946
<Default><b>[tense music]</b></Default>

358
00:13:28,970 --> 00:13:34,405
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

359
00:13:34,429 --> 00:13:37,326
<Default><b>The hydra seems to only
be targeting Raphtalia.</b></Default>

360
00:13:37,350 --> 00:13:39,086
<Default><b>My best guess
is that she probably</b></Default>

361
00:13:39,110 --> 00:13:42,005
<Default><b>reminds the hydra of the
emperor that sealed it away.</b></Default>

362
00:13:42,029 --> 00:13:43,686
<Default><b>I'm not sure
I like that.</b></Default>

363
00:13:43,710 --> 00:13:46,346
<Default><b>We could use the fact that
it's targeting her to lure</b></Default>

364
00:13:46,370 --> 00:13:48,056
<Default><b>it away from
here, but...</b></Default>

365
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:50,436
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Yeah, but there's
no way to nullify the hydra's</b></Default>

366
00:13:50,460 --> 00:13:52,275
<Default><b>protection
without Raphtalia.</b></Default>

367
00:13:52,299 --> 00:13:54,466
<Default><b>There's enough of us
here to handle it.</b></Default>

368
00:13:54,490 --> 00:13:57,336
<Default><b>And we have a strong army
here to help us, too.</b></Default>

369
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:58,806
<Default><b>Oh, right.</b></Default>

370
00:13:58,830 --> 00:14:00,265
<Default><b>Fine, then.</b></Default>

371
00:14:00,289 --> 00:14:03,495
<Default><b>Raphtalia, Sadeena</b></Default>

372
00:14:03,519 --> 00:14:05,135
<Default><b>you're coming with me.</b></Default>

373
00:14:05,159 --> 00:14:07,846
<Default><b>The rest of you</b></Default>

374
00:14:07,870 --> 00:14:10,306
<Default><b>We need you
to buy us time, not kill it!</b></Default>

375
00:14:10,330 --> 00:14:11,775
<Default><b>Understood.</b></Default>

376
00:14:11,799 --> 00:14:14,596
<Default><b>Yeah, 'cause I definitely
planned on killing it.</b></Default>

377
00:14:14,620 --> 00:14:17,206
<Default><b>Oh, why did I have to throw
away my weapon earlier?</b></Default>

378
00:14:17,230 --> 00:14:19,806
<Default><b>I'll be right here
to provide you backup, Atla.</b></Default>

379
00:14:19,830 --> 00:14:22,125
<Default><b>We're here to help you
however we can.</b></Default>

380
00:14:22,149 --> 00:14:24,976
<Default><b>Quick, one of you go
and evacuate the town.</b></Default>

381
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,655
<Default><b>Yes, sir!</b></Default>

382
00:14:26,679 --> 00:14:28,590
<Default><b>[growls]</b></Default>

383
00:14:30,029 --> 00:14:31,235
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Let's go!</b></Default>

384
00:14:31,259 --> 00:14:33,905
<Default><b>Zweit Thunder Burst!</b></Default>

385
00:14:33,929 --> 00:14:35,169
<Default><b>Meteor Shot!</b></Default>

386
00:14:36,350 --> 00:14:37,910
<Default><b>[lightning crackles]</b></Default>

387
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:50,905
<Default><b>[coughs]</b></Default>

388
00:14:50,929 --> 00:14:52,796
<Default><b>Are you OK, Raphtalia?</b></Default>

389
00:14:52,820 --> 00:14:54,060
<Default><b>Yes, barely.</b></Default>

390
00:14:55,259 --> 00:14:58,166
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] It's not magic</b></Default>

391
00:14:58,190 --> 00:14:59,735
<Default><b>terrible in
the air here.</b></Default>

392
00:14:59,759 --> 00:15:01,916
<Default><b>We can't stay too long.</b></Default>

393
00:15:01,940 --> 00:15:06,025
<Default><b>Whatever it is, it's taking
over this protective barrier.</b></Default>

394
00:15:06,049 --> 00:15:09,086
<Default><b>We have to hurry before
they end up freeing any</b></Default>

395
00:15:09,110 --> 00:15:10,655
<Default><b>of the other
sealed beasts.</b></Default>

396
00:15:10,679 --> 00:15:12,035
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Damn it.</b></Default>

397
00:15:12,059 --> 00:15:14,365
<Default><b>The government here
really is run by idiots.</b></Default>

398
00:15:14,389 --> 00:15:15,389
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

399
00:15:17,379 --> 00:15:20,336
<Default><b>[mysterious music]</b></Default>

400
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:21,696
<Default><b>I can read this.</b></Default>

401
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,720
<Default><b>Is this the hero
language, then?</b></Default>

402
00:15:25,399 --> 00:15:28,826
<Default><b>"How to strengthen
the cardinal shield weapon."</b></Default>

403
00:15:28,850 --> 00:15:30,686
<Default><b>[humming]</b></Default>

404
00:15:30,710 --> 00:15:32,110
<Default><b>[shimmering]</b></Default>

405
00:15:34,909 --> 00:15:36,875
<Default><b>I'm sensing magic.</b></Default>

406
00:15:36,899 --> 00:15:38,976
<Default><b>I'll read the
rest out loud.</b></Default>

407
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:42,125
<Default><b>"How to strengthen the cardinal
shield weapon, method one.</b></Default>

408
00:15:42,149 --> 00:15:44,005
<Default><b>Share the methods
of getting stronger</b></Default>

409
00:15:44,029 --> 00:15:46,789
<Default><b>with the other cardinal
weapons or vassal weapons."</b></Default>

410
00:15:50,340 --> 00:15:51,995
<Default><b>I already knew that.</b></Default>

411
00:15:52,019 --> 00:15:53,885
<Default><b>This is worthless.</b></Default>

412
00:15:53,909 --> 00:15:56,586
<Default><b>But is that
everything it says?</b></Default>

413
00:15:56,610 --> 00:15:58,696
<Default><b>Maybe if Ren
or Itsuki reads it</b></Default>

414
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,525
<Default><b>it'll say something
different.</b></Default>

415
00:16:00,549 --> 00:16:02,669
<Default><b>I'll have to bring
them here later.</b></Default>

416
00:16:06,470 --> 00:16:08,745
<Default><b>[humming]</b></Default>

417
00:16:08,769 --> 00:16:10,259
<Default><b>Is it below?</b></Default>

418
00:16:12,389 --> 00:16:13,605
<Default><b>No, it's not!</b></Default>

419
00:16:13,629 --> 00:16:15,615
<Default><b>Everyone stand back!</b></Default>

420
00:16:15,639 --> 00:16:17,056
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

421
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:18,505
<Default><b>Ah!</b></Default>

422
00:16:18,529 --> 00:16:20,450
<Default><b>[splash]</b></Default>

423
00:16:24,299 --> 00:16:26,056
<Default><b>That was awfully close.</b></Default>

424
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:28,275
<Default><b>What a waste of time
that was.</b></Default>

425
00:16:28,299 --> 00:16:29,645
<Default><b>[GAELION] Not quite.</b></Default>

426
00:16:29,669 --> 00:16:32,416
<Default><b>After all, the real one
is coming out now.</b></Default>

427
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:34,365
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

428
00:16:34,389 --> 00:16:37,809
<Default><b>[thrilling music]</b></Default>

429
00:16:40,259 --> 00:16:43,926
<Default><b>The purple light glowing from
its body must be the core.</b></Default>

430
00:16:43,950 --> 00:16:46,405
<Default><b>So we have to repeat
what we did before?</b></Default>

431
00:16:46,429 --> 00:16:47,966
<Default><b>[GAELION]
This one is stronger.</b></Default>

432
00:16:47,990 --> 00:16:49,995
<Default><b>It appears to be
gradually absorbing</b></Default>

433
00:16:50,019 --> 00:16:53,655
<Default><b>the power that dispersed
into the Dragon Veins.</b></Default>

434
00:16:53,679 --> 00:16:55,426
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Sorry, but I don't
know how much longer we</b></Default>

435
00:16:55,450 --> 00:16:57,285
<Default><b>can hold this one back.</b></Default>

436
00:16:57,309 --> 00:16:58,405
<Default><b>You heard the girl.</b></Default>

437
00:16:58,429 --> 00:16:59,755
<Default><b>Let's hurry it up.</b></Default>

438
00:16:59,779 --> 00:17:01,645
<Default><b>After all, you like
things done fast</b></Default>

439
00:17:01,669 --> 00:17:03,255
<Default><b>and without
causing a fuss</b></Default>

440
00:17:03,279 --> 00:17:05,366
<Default><b>What's got you
so cooperative?</b></Default>

441
00:17:05,390 --> 00:17:07,906
<Default><b>I always am</b></Default>

442
00:17:07,930 --> 00:17:10,035
<Default><b>to rule this
country, Naofumi.</b></Default>

443
00:17:10,059 --> 00:17:12,146
<Default><b>I don't want it
getting ruined.</b></Default>

444
00:17:12,170 --> 00:17:15,926
<Default><b>Well, I don't know if I'll
be the one who's ruling it.</b></Default>

445
00:17:15,950 --> 00:17:19,295
<Default><b>[SADEENA] Either way, I just
want to help however I can.</b></Default>

446
00:17:19,319 --> 00:17:22,696
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Good, 'cause
I need your help right now.</b></Default>

447
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:23,697
<Default><b>Sadeena.</b></Default>

448
00:17:23,721 --> 00:17:25,166
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

449
00:17:25,190 --> 00:17:26,636
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] You can do
a beast transformation too.</b></Default>

450
00:17:26,660 --> 00:17:28,126
<Default><b>- Oh, my.
- [NAOFUMI] Want to try?</b></Default>

451
00:17:28,150 --> 00:17:29,456
<Default><b>[SADEENA] Of course.</b></Default>

452
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:31,126
<Default><b>Is there any
other choice?</b></Default>

453
00:17:31,150 --> 00:17:32,696
<Default><b>OK, let's do this.</b></Default>

454
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:35,255
<Default><b>Sakura Sphere
of Influence!</b></Default>

455
00:17:35,279 --> 00:17:37,206
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

456
00:17:37,230 --> 00:17:40,626
<Default><b>[mystical music]</b></Default>

457
00:17:40,650 --> 00:17:47,650
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

458
00:17:53,369 --> 00:17:54,666
<Default><b>Amazing!</b></Default>

459
00:17:54,690 --> 00:17:58,116
<Default><b>I can feel power
flowing through my body!</b></Default>

460
00:17:58,140 --> 00:18:01,085
<Default><b>It must be
Naofumi's love!</b></Default>

461
00:18:01,109 --> 00:18:03,735
<Default><b>Is that really what she
looks like when transformed?</b></Default>

462
00:18:03,759 --> 00:18:06,575
<Default><b>I can sense her power
from here.</b></Default>

463
00:18:06,599 --> 00:18:09,575
<Default><b>[SADEENA] I think I can hear
the Water Dragon's voice.</b></Default>

464
00:18:09,599 --> 00:18:11,285
<Default><b>I feel unstoppable!</b></Default>

465
00:18:11,309 --> 00:18:12,985
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Then quit
yapping and do something!</b></Default>

466
00:18:13,009 --> 00:18:14,646
<Default><b>[SADEENA] I'm on it.</b></Default>

467
00:18:14,670 --> 00:18:17,136
<Default><b>Oh, is this
how I say it?</b></Default>

468
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:18,726
<Default><b>Thunder God!</b></Default>

469
00:18:18,750 --> 00:18:21,515
<Default><b>[thunder cracking]</b></Default>

470
00:18:21,539 --> 00:18:23,569
<Default><b>And now Sea God!</b></Default>

471
00:18:24,710 --> 00:18:26,555
<Default><b>[chittering]</b></Default>

472
00:18:26,579 --> 00:18:30,815
<Default><b>Is this the true form
of the Water Dragon's miko?</b></Default>

473
00:18:30,839 --> 00:18:32,839
<Default><b>It's like a battle
of the gods.</b></Default>

474
00:18:33,630 --> 00:18:36,005
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Let's finish this, Raphtalia!</b></Default>

475
00:18:36,029 --> 00:18:37,606
<Default><b>Right!</b></Default>

476
00:18:37,630 --> 00:18:39,106
<Default><b>[electric crackle]</b></Default>

477
00:18:39,130 --> 00:18:45,976
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

478
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:48,230
<Default><b>Supreme Ultimate
Slash of Destiny!</b></Default>

479
00:18:49,799 --> 00:18:50,776
<Default><b>Nice!</b></Default>

480
00:18:50,800 --> 00:18:52,005
<Default><b>Its protection's gone.</b></Default>

481
00:18:52,029 --> 00:18:53,006
<Default><b>Finish it!</b></Default>

482
00:18:53,030 --> 00:18:56,835
<Default><b>[epic music]</b></Default>

483
00:18:56,859 --> 00:19:00,676
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

484
00:19:00,700 --> 00:19:03,916
<Default><b>Kagura Dance of Sakura</b></Default>

485
00:19:03,940 --> 00:19:10,940
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

486
00:19:20,910 --> 00:19:21,910
<Default><b>Ah.</b></Default>

487
00:19:23,740 --> 00:19:25,606
<Default><b>I... incredible.</b></Default>

488
00:19:25,630 --> 00:19:28,095
<Default><b>With these
folks leading us</b></Default>

489
00:19:28,119 --> 00:19:31,696
<Default><b>and their evil advisor
Makina won't stand a chance!</b></Default>

490
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:34,906
<Default><b>Stand proud and let
loose the victory cry!</b></Default>

491
00:19:34,930 --> 00:19:38,680
<Default><b>[soldiers chant
and laugh]</b></Default>

492
00:19:45,319 --> 00:19:47,906
<Default><b>I have no doubt in my mind
that this is supposed</b></Default>

493
00:19:47,930 --> 00:19:49,610
<Default><b>to be the hydra's core.</b></Default>

494
00:19:50,839 --> 00:19:52,719
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
But it's a sword.</b></Default>

495
00:19:53,869 --> 00:19:56,785
<Default><b>The cursed blade
of Ama-no-Murakumo.</b></Default>

496
00:19:56,809 --> 00:19:59,696
<Default><b>Just touching it would
be enough to curse you.</b></Default>

497
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:02,376
<Default><b>Well, if that's the case</b></Default>

498
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:03,646
<Default><b>So what do we do?</b></Default>

499
00:20:03,670 --> 00:20:06,055
<Default><b>[MURAMASA]
Oh, looks like you got it!</b></Default>

500
00:20:06,079 --> 00:20:08,075
<Default><b>[ELHART]
That was amazing.</b></Default>

501
00:20:08,099 --> 00:20:11,095
<Default><b>Look, I had heard rumors that
your fights can get pretty</b></Default>

502
00:20:11,119 --> 00:20:13,186
<Default><b>intense, but
that was insane!</b></Default>

503
00:20:13,210 --> 00:20:14,686
<Default><b>No kidding.</b></Default>

504
00:20:14,710 --> 00:20:18,156
<Default><b>[MURAMASA] Wow, that blade
sure looks mighty sharp.</b></Default>

505
00:20:18,180 --> 00:20:20,420
<Default><b>This must be
the hydra's real body.</b></Default>

506
00:20:23,059 --> 00:20:24,396
<Default><b>Wait!</b></Default>

507
00:20:24,420 --> 00:20:26,759
<Default><b>[mystical music]</b></Default>

508
00:20:28,170 --> 00:20:29,196
<Default><b>Oh, shut up.</b></Default>

509
00:20:29,220 --> 00:20:30,540
<Default><b>Calm yourself.</b></Default>

510
00:20:32,369 --> 00:20:35,466
<Default><b>[sighs] This thing's
packing a serious curse</b></Default>

511
00:20:35,490 --> 00:20:37,466
<Default><b>so we can't
use it for a while.</b></Default>

512
00:20:37,490 --> 00:20:40,535
<Default><b>How are you just holding it
without getting cursed?</b></Default>

513
00:20:40,559 --> 00:20:42,325
<Default><b>I am a blacksmith,
aren't I?</b></Default>

514
00:20:42,349 --> 00:20:45,116
<Default><b>And blacksmiths don't allow
weapons to curse them.</b></Default>

515
00:20:45,140 --> 00:20:46,795
<Default><b>That's my master for ya!</b></Default>

516
00:20:46,819 --> 00:20:50,426
<Default><b>OK, can you make sure it
doesn't go out of control then?</b></Default>

517
00:20:50,450 --> 00:20:53,055
<Default><b>[scoffs]
That's not my problem!</b></Default>

518
00:20:53,079 --> 00:20:56,755
<Default><b>It may not affect you</b></Default>

519
00:20:56,779 --> 00:20:58,345
<Default><b>then people will suffer.</b></Default>

520
00:20:58,369 --> 00:21:00,505
<Default><b>I just wish you
had asked me earlier.</b></Default>

521
00:21:00,529 --> 00:21:03,146
<Default><b>I'd be honored to be
of service, young lady.</b></Default>

522
00:21:03,170 --> 00:21:04,815
<Default><b>What an idiot.</b></Default>

523
00:21:04,839 --> 00:21:07,906
<Default><b>Anyway, now that
the hydra's taken care of</b></Default>

524
00:21:07,930 --> 00:21:10,815
<Default><b>we have to make sure the whole
country knows about it</b></Default>

525
00:21:10,839 --> 00:21:13,755
<Default><b>that they hear all about how
the revolutionary army and</b></Default>

526
00:21:13,779 --> 00:21:17,146
<Default><b>their new emperor destroyed the
government's monster before it</b></Default>

527
00:21:17,170 --> 00:21:18,896
<Default><b>was able to hurt anyone.</b></Default>

528
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:21,920
<Default><b>[chuckles] So we're the good
guys who saved the day, huh?</b></Default>

529
00:21:23,710 --> 00:21:25,406
<Default><b>It's just a performance.</b></Default>

530
00:21:25,430 --> 00:21:28,636
<Default><b>No one's actually making
you become emperor.</b></Default>

531
00:21:28,660 --> 00:21:30,599
<Default><b>Yeah, I guess not.</b></Default>

532
00:21:31,930 --> 00:21:34,636
<Default><b>[RALUVA]
Is this... sorry, I've been</b></Default>

533
00:21:34,660 --> 00:21:36,805
<Default><b>wondering since before
the battle started.</b></Default>

534
00:21:36,829 --> 00:21:39,956
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Yes, she is</b></Default>

535
00:21:39,980 --> 00:21:41,166
<Default><b>Sure am!</b></Default>

536
00:21:41,190 --> 00:21:43,085
<Default><b>My name is Filo.
Nice to meet you.</b></Default>

537
00:21:43,109 --> 00:21:46,676
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] She gets special
powers if a hero raises her.</b></Default>

538
00:21:46,700 --> 00:21:48,416
<Default><b>Incredible.</b></Default>

539
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:49,946
<Default><b>That white form.</b></Default>

540
00:21:49,970 --> 00:21:52,595
<Default><b>A Filolial with
a sakura-colored pattern!</b></Default>

541
00:21:52,619 --> 00:21:55,835
<Default><b>It's so perfect and will only
help serve to our advantage</b></Default>

542
00:21:55,859 --> 00:21:57,019
<Default><b>even more.</b></Default>

543
00:21:58,799 --> 00:22:00,265
<Default><b>[soft flute music]</b></Default>

544
00:22:00,289 --> 00:22:01,765
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

545
00:22:01,789 --> 00:22:02,789
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

546
00:22:04,789 --> 00:22:08,255
<Default><b>[theme music
and Japanese singing]</b></Default>

547
00:22:08,279 --> 00:22:09,779
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

548
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:39,000
<Default><b>EPISODE 9: ZODIA</b></Default>

